title: started playing during preseason
body:
i've only played season 8 preseason and not season 7, will my preseason 8 rank matter for my placements right now or it will just be a normal new account placements system.

(why am i on oce)

replies.body: Preseason only has a minimal effect, so for the most part unless you were significantly higher or lower in preseason it'll just be normal new account placements.
